🛠️ Step 6 – Trap Signals
#!/bin/bash

trap "echo 'Script interrupted'; exit" SIGINT

while true
do
    echo "Running..."
    sleep 2
done

Press Ctrl + C to test the trap.

💻 Mini Project – Backup Script

Create backup.sh

#!/bin/bash

SOURCE="$HOME/Documents"
DEST="$HOME/backups"

mkdir -p "$DEST"

tar -czf "$DEST/backup-$(date +%F-%H%M).tar.gz" "$SOURCE"

echo "Backup Completed Successfully"
