🧠 Senior DevOps Challenge

Create a script named health-monitor.sh that:

Checks:
CPU usage
Memory usage
Disk usage
Writes all results to logs/health.log.
If disk usage exceeds 80%, print a warning.
If disk usage exceeds 90%, exit with code 1.
Add timestamps to every log entry.

Example log:

2026-07-03 10:15:22 INFO Starting health check
2026-07-03 10:15:22 INFO CPU Usage: 18%
2026-07-03 10:15:22 INFO Memory Usage: 42%
2026-07-03 10:15:22 WARNING Disk usage on / is 84%
2026-07-03 10:15:22 INFO Health check completed
