🔥 Production Scenario

Problem: A nightly backup job completed, but no backup file was created.

Investigation
Check the log file:
cat logs/backup.log
Verify the source directory exists:
ls -ld "$HOME/Documents"
Check destination permissions:
ls -ld "$HOME/backups"
Test the tar command manually:
tar -tzf backup-file.tar.gz
Verify available disk space:
df -h
